                                Small Business Appointment Scheduler (SBAS) is a software as a service (SaaS) product that allows sole 
                                proprietors to schedule appointments with their clients. This system allows business owners to track 
                                inventory, accept payments, invoice clients and provide feedback to clients when services are completed 
                                as well as when services will be performed. What sets SBAS apart from the rest is our scheduling 
                                algorithm that verifies appointments can be scheduled or rescheduled based on distance and 
                                time from location to location based on any previous and following appointments.
                            </p>
